---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PhotoModal from '../components/PhotoModal.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  active="about"
  description="Ethan Manzi, KD3BQP — Technician-class amateur radio operator based in York, PA. Radios, digital modes, and life from the shack."
>
  <div class="layout">
    <main class="main">
      <div class="mono eyebrow faint">About the operator</div>
      <h1 class="serif heading">Introduce yourself to Ethan Manzi, KD3BQP</h1>

      <div class="photo photo-placeholder">[ PHOTO &mdash; the operator at the bench ]</div>

      <p class="body-text">
        Hai! My name is Ethan Manzi, I'm a <span id="dyvar-age">23</span> year old HAM operator, with intrests in radio
        <i>(of course)</i>, computer science (programming), and going for walks. I got my license back in 2024, first
        getting my GMRS license, and then quickly thereafter, I upgraded to my Technician-class HAM license.
      </p>
      <p class="body-text">
        I try and participate in my local club, the <strong>Keystone VHF Club (W3HZU)</strong>, and with my local
        ARES/RACES/Skywarn/AUXCOM group, called <strong>YARS</strong> up here. I've tried POTA a couple times, but have
        yet to <i>really</i> get into it. Mostly operate near my house, but often not <i>inside it</i>, because most of
        my antenna are mobile antennas, and I don't have the ground connection and such yet.
      </p>
      <p class="body-text">
        This is my personal blog, for sharing my experiences, findings, and revewing the products that I buy, to
        hopefully give others resources to decide if its worth getting for them too. I also host myself a logbook,
        and a few other utilities, since I have the domain anyways! If you got something to say, you're more than
        welcome to <a href="/contact">contact me</a>!
      </p>

      <h2 class="serif subheading">What you&rsquo;ll find here</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Blog posts about events that I work</li>
        <li>Reviews of products I purchase, receive, or use</li>
        <li>My opinions and experiences doing general HAM operations</li>
      </ul>
    </main>

    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="who-card">
        <button type="button" class="photo-btn" data-photo-trigger aria-label="View photo of Ethan">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.kd3bqp.radio/blogphotos/IMG_3437.jpeg"
            alt="Ethan — KD3BQP"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
          />
        </button>
        <div class="who">
          <div class="serif who-name">Ethan</div>
          <div class="mono who-call">KD3BQP &middot; WSHI362</div>
          <div class="serif who-loc">York, PA &middot; Grid FM19px</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="mono panel-title accent">The station</div>
        <dl class="mono dl">
          <div class="row"><dt class="faint small">DAILY HT</dt><dd>BTech UV-PRO</dd></div>
          <div class="row"><dt class="faint small">BACKUP HT</dt><dd>Explorer QRZ-1</dd></div>
          <div class="row"><dt class="faint small">BASE STATION</dt><dd>Yaesu FT991-A</dd></div>
          <div class="row last"><dt class="faint small">ANTENNAS</dt><dd>2m/70cm Slim Jim, mag-mount mobile</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="mono panel-title faint">Where to find me</div>
        <div class="find-me mono">
          <a href="https://www.qrz.com/db/KD3BQP" target="_blank" rel="noopener">QRZ &rarr; KD3BQP</a>
          <a href="#">Mastodon &rarr; @kd3bqp</a>
          <a href="/contact">Email the shack</a>
        </div>
        <div class="club-note mono">YARS &middot; York, PA<br />Net: Mondays &middot; 2m FM</div>
        <div class="club-note mono">On the Air<br />Usually monitoring 2m &amp; 70cm</div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <PhotoModal />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .layout {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 40px 0 8px;
  }
  .main {
    flex: 1 1 460px;
    min-width: 0;
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .faint {
    color: var(--faint);
  }
  .heading {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 38px;
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .photo {
    height: 260px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .body-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .body-text strong {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .body-text a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .subheading {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 30px 0 14px;
  }
  .list {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    padding-left: 22px;
  }
  .list li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .sidebar {
    flex: 1 1 280px;
    max-width: 320px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 24px;
  }
  .who-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 15px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 26px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .photo-btn {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    line-height: 0;
  }
  .photo-btn:hover img {
    opacity: 0.82;
  }
  .photo-btn img {
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    border-radius: 13px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .who-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 23px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .who-call {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 7px;
  }
  .who-loc {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .panel {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .panel-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .accent {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .dl {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .row {
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .row.last {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .row dt.small {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .row dd {
    margin: 3px 0 0;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .find-me {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .find-me a {
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .find-me a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .club-note {
    margin-top: 15px;
    padding-top: 13px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
